QuestData.Title: Lost and Lonely
QuestData.Description: The starving, mangy dog whines piteously and attempts a brief wag of its tail.$B$BIt looks like it could use a good meal right about now.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 20 Tasty T-Bone from the Skyrange Mushan on the Skyrange in the Valley of the Four Winds.
QuestData.RewardText: The dog perks its ears up at the sight of the juicy steak.$B$BAs soon as you throw it down, the dog starts eating ravenously.
